    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>由于最近用<a href="https://www.vmware.com/cn/products/workstation-pro/workstation-pro-evaluation.html">vmware workstation</a> linux编译openwrt,导致单个虚拟磁盘文件过大，故分开存储Linux系统文件和openwrt编译文件。</p><h2 id="初步准备"><a href="#初步准备" class="headerlink" title="初步准备"></a>初步准备</h2><h3 id="Vmware-workstation新建虚拟磁盘"><a href="#Vmware-workstation新建虚拟磁盘" class="headerlink" title="Vmware workstation新建虚拟磁盘"></a>Vmware workstation新建虚拟磁盘</h3><p><img src="/img/%E8%AE%B0%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1vmware%E7%BB%99Linux%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E7%A1%AC%E7%9B%98/vmware_disk.jpg"></p><h3 id="使用df命令产看当前系统已挂载的磁盘"><a href="#使用df命令产看当前系统已挂载的磁盘" class="headerlink" title="使用df命令产看当前系统已挂载的磁盘"></a>使用df命令产看当前系统已挂载的磁盘</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">df</span> -h</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/img/%E8%AE%B0%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1vmware%E7%BB%99Linux%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E7%A1%AC%E7%9B%98/df_command.jpg"></p><h3 id="2-使用fdisk命令查看所有分区"><a href="#2-使用fdisk命令查看所有分区" class="headerlink" title="2.使用fdisk命令查看所有分区"></a>2.使用fdisk命令查看所有分区</h3><blockquote><p>找到我们新加的盘符</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo fdisk -l</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/img/%E8%AE%B0%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1vmware%E7%BB%99Linux%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E7%A1%AC%E7%9B%98/fdisk_l_command.jpg"></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
